OL,4,G1210FA New Life in the Sun
OL,5,     GAfter a long renovation, Tom and
OL,6,     GTerry trial-run their vegan B&B
OL,7,     Gin Spain. And in Portugal,
OL,8,     Gdreamers Louise and Shay find out
OL,9,     Gif they can make it all a reality.
OL,10,G1310FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GThe B&B battle begins at the
OL,12,     GMayfield Hotel in Seaburn,
OL,13,     GSunderland. There's cause for
OL,14,     Gapplause when a seal makes an
OL,15,     Gappearance, but some guests get
OL,16,     Gpicky about the paintwork.
OL,17,G1345FFour in a Bed
OL,18,     GThe B&Bers descend on Gateshead
OL,19,     Gfor the week's second visit, at
OL,20,     GSutherlands Hotel, where two
OL,21,     Gguests want revenge and are
OL,22,     Gdetermined to dig up some dirt.
